<paragraph blockId="10.[160,1156,1070,1200]" box="[160,409,1070,1096]" pageId="10" pageNumber="275">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,409,1070,1096]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="275">External morphology</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="10.[160,1156,1070,1200]" pageId="10" pageNumber="275">Body short, thick, background colour black with numerous white papillae. Mantle margin white. Rhinophores with lamellae, beige or white. Branchial leaves dark brown.</paragraph>
